  *octal-digit*  \n  \n **\\\\**  *octal-digit octal-digit*  \n  \n **\\\\**  *octal-digit octal-digit octal-digit*  \n  \n *hexadecimal-escape-sequence*:  \n **\\x**  *hexadecimal-digit*  \n  \n *hexadecimal-escape-sequence hexadecimal-digit*  \n  \n## See Also  \n [C Constants](../c-language/c-constants.md)"}